trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls used to track and manage related groups of controls.
trans-unit.target: Contém uma coleção de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> controles usados para controlar e gerenciar grupos de controles.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartCollection class is a read-only collection of controls, typically used by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> controls to manage sets of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: A classe WebPartCollection é uma coleção somente leitura de controles, normalmente usado por <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controles para gerenciar conjuntos de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses a WebPartCollection object to keep a list of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls on a page, whereas a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> control uses a WebPartCollection object to track the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls that it contains.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controle usa um objeto de WebPartCollection para manter uma lista de todos os <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles em uma página, enquanto um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>controle usa um objeto WebPartCollection para controlar o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles que ele contém.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The WebPartCollection collection contains both <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls and other server controls (such as user controls, custom controls, and ASP.NET controls) that are placed in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zones and used as part of Web Parts applications.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > WebPartCollection a coleção contém <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles e outros controles de servidor (como controles de usuário, controles personalizados e controles do ASP.NET) que são colocados em <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>zonas e usados como parte de aplicativos Web Parts.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: So, for example, if you have a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> zone in a page, and within it you declare a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control and the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar> control, both controls will be in the WebPartCollection collection referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Assim, por exemplo, se você tiver um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>zonas em uma página, e nele você declarar um personalizado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controle e o ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar>controle, ambos os controles estará na coleção WebPartCollection referenciada pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartCollection object exists so that the Web Parts control set can work with strongly typed collections.
trans-unit.target: O objeto WebPartCollection existe para que o conjunto de controles de Web Parts pode trabalhar com coleções fortemente tipadas.

trans-unit.source: Similarly, if you want to perform mass operations on a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, you can get a reference to a WebPartCollection object using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Da mesma forma, se você deseja executar operações em massa em um conjunto de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles, você pode obter uma referência a um objeto WebPartCollection usando o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: For example, you might want to loop through all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls on a page and change their appearance in some way.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, talvez você queira repetir todos os <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles em uma página e alterar a aparência de alguma forma.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Even though the WebPartCollection object is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the properties of the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Mesmo que o objeto WebPartCollection é somente leitura, você pode fazer alterações programáticas para as propriedades dos controles subjacentes referenciado na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância vazia do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartCollection constructor initializes an empty instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor de WebPartCollection inicializa uma instância vazia da <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>classe.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: The object itself is read-only and has no method to add individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls to it; therefore, you will have little occasion to use this constructor.
trans-unit.target: O próprio objeto é somente leitura e não tem nenhum método para adicionar individuais <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles a ela; portanto, você terá pouco ocasião para usar este construtor.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"></xref> object by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância de um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"> </xref> objeto passando um <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>coleção de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> controles.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartCollection constructor initializes an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> class by passing in a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: O construtor de WebPartCollection inicializa uma instância do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>classe, passando uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: Although a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object is read-only and there is no method for adding individual controls to it, you can create your own <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of controls, and pass that to the WebPartCollection constructor.
trans-unit.target: Embora um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objeto é somente leitura e não há nenhum método para adicionar controles individuais a ele, você pode criar seus próprios <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>coleção de controles e passá-lo para o construtor WebPartCollection.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: This enables you to create custom collections and perform bulk operations on them.
trans-unit.target: Isso permite que você crie coleções personalizadas e executar operações em massa neles.

trans-unit.source: You can also access the underlying controls in the collection and change their property values programmatically.
trans-unit.target: Você também pode acessar os controles subjacentes na coleção e alterar seus valores de propriedade programaticamente.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> controles.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular control exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor que indica se um determinado controle existe na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The Contains method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> object and determine whether it is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: O método contém permite que você verifique se um determinado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>do objeto e determinar se ele é parte de um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objeto.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> que é verificada para determinar se ele está na coleção.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular control is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um valor booliano que indica se um determinado controle está na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Copia a coleção para uma matriz de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object, a subset of those controls, or a superset of those controls.
trans-unit.target: O método CopyTo é útil quando você deseja montar uma matriz personalizada que contém o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controla no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objeto, um subconjunto desses controles ou um subconjunto desses controles.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> objects to contain the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> objetos para conter a coleção copiada.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: O ponto de partida na matriz na qual colocar o conteúdo da coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna a posição de um membro específico da coleção.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method is useful if you have multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls on a Web Parts page, and you need to know the ordinal position of one control relative to the others.
trans-unit.target: O método IndexOf será útil se você tiver vários <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles em uma página de Web Parts e você precisam saber a posição ordinal de um controle em relação a outras pessoas.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> that is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> que é um membro da coleção.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um inteiro que indica a posição de um objeto específico da coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns a member of the collection based on its position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um membro da coleção com base em sua posição na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The Item indexer allows you to access the underlying <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object by index, and change their property values or call methods.
trans-unit.target: O indexador de Item permite que você acesse subjacente <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controles em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>por índice, do objeto e alterar seus valores de propriedade ou chamar métodos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The index of a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control in a collection.
trans-unit.target: O índice de um determinado <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> controle em uma coleção.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> no índice especificado na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns a member of the collection based on a unique string identifier.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um membro da coleção com base em um identificador de cadeia de caracteres exclusiva.

trans-unit.source: The Item indexer enables you to access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object according to a unique identifier.
trans-unit.target: O indexador de Item permite que você acesse um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controlar uma <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objeto de acordo com um identificador exclusivo.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The Web Parts control set performs case-insensitive matching on this property, so case sensitivity is not part of a unique `id` value.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > O conjunto executa a correspondência diferencia maiusculas de minúsculas nessa propriedade para diferenciação de maiusculas e minúsculas não seja parte de uma única `id` valor.

trans-unit.source: The Item property also works to identify members of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection> object in some specialized cases.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade do Item também funciona para identificar membros de um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>objeto em alguns casos especializados.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection>

trans-unit.source: In the case of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> controls, the indexer is able to match the identifier for the underlying child control wrapped by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: No caso de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>controles, o indexador é capaz de corresponder ao identificador para o controle filho subjacente encapsulado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>

trans-unit.source: In the case of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart> controls, the indexer matches the identifier for the control based on a case-insensitive comparison of the `id` parameter and either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.OriginalID%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.GenericWebPartID%2A> property values.
trans-unit.target: No caso de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart>controles, o indexador coincidir com o identificador para o controle com base em uma comparação entre maiusculas e minúsculas de `id` parâmetro e uma a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.OriginalID%2A>ou <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.GenericWebPartID%2A>valores de propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.GenericWebPartID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart.OriginalID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPart>

trans-unit.source: The unique identifier for a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control in a collection.
trans-unit.target: O identificador exclusivo para um determinado <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> controle em uma coleção.

trans-unit.source: The first in the collection whose ID equals the value of id.
trans-unit.target: A primeira na coleção cuja ID igual ao valor de id .
